The paper presents an algorithm for solving the maximum flow problem and related problems, which are fundamental problems in computer science and optimization. The algorithm involves the development and application of a new general interior point method, which is likely to be of interest to researchers in the areas of data structures (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational complexity (cs.CC), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and machine learning (cs.LG).
